accessibility.text: LED Tower and LED columns react to the people when they move near by. Visitors can interact with media screens, for example, find their silhouettes appearing under the waterfall engage in virtual painting of a large scale by their movements or change speed, direction, sizes and forms of visual content.
Interactive visualizations use videos / animated images or close-up footage mapped on LED Tower sides, floor screens and columns, blob tracking helps adding interactivity that reacts to passers by.
Visuals are only mood references,  original content will be designed.
